des:
Work out with Alexa and us, your sassy One Minute Workout coach throughout the week. Each day is a different workout. No skipping!

Once you open the skill, just ask Alexa to start the workout. You can also ask Alexa for your progress.

This skill was created by Trey in SF using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer. And please, consider working out for more than just 1 minute per day, and always consult with a doctor before starting any exercise regimine.
